9 An Act relating to definitions and general
provisions; amending 25 O.S. 2021, Section 106, which
10 relates to newspapers; defining term; prescribing
requirements; imposing duties upon periodical and
11 nonperiodical newspapers; imposing restrictions based
on geographical location; modifying certain
12 publication provisions; modifying provisions related
to excusable failure with respect to continuity of
13 publication; and providing an effective date.
