16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 25 O.S. 2021, Section 106, is
18 amended to read as follows:
19 Section 106. No legal notice, advertisement, or publication of
20 any kind required or provided for by the laws of this state to be
21 published in a newspaper of general circulation shall have force or
22 effect unless published in a legal newspaper of the county in this
23 state. Legal newspapers shall be either:
